{
  "stem": "5356.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "On Monday, they went to another one, to Sandomierz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Thursday, they went to Lagow and things like that because, otherwise, just sitting at home, they couldn't have made their living not going out and trying to sell their merchandise.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had six people in the house working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was producing boots, and most of our business was done with farmers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had like this-- I mean, a clientele for 20, 30 years with the same people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They come in, then my father knew what they need.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we didn't go any place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father didn't travel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything was in the house because we had a big enough place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The house consisted of, you know, two bedrooms, a big room, and then a kitchen, and then one place-- it was like a front after this, where the-- where the work was done.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Two of my brothers worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had about two-- two other guys-- Gentile guys, Christian-- but they worked for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was all the years that I remember, what-- what was done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The-- the city was pleasant place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, there were nice buildings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were small-- I mean, two or three-- two stories was the tallest building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There wasn't any high buildings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had a case where-- what I said, Rabbi [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Scheuer ?] Heschel had was a synagogue which was upstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was a story when during the 1700s, when the Hasidim were coming down, Friday night, from the services, their hats were thrown off by the demons or something like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he asked to-- they should take a piece of steel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they engraved his name, and they put down on the top of the-- the attic in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
